   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Flavius . . ., strategos of the . . . nome, from Apollonios, secretary of the metropolis. In reference to the letter written to you by his excellency Ulpius Serenianus, the archiereus, on the . . . of Phamenoth of the 14th year, concerning Tastoous daughter of Apollonios, who had promised to make an entreaty before him (about) 2 1/2 arourai near . . ., in answer to your inquiry, I report that Tastoous is in Alexandria.;The 14th year of Imperator Caesar Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Augustus Armeniacus Medicus Parthicus Germanicus Maximus. Mesore 10.</ab>
         </div>
